page.title: 12Wild Flowers and Plants
page.content: Lots of plants grow in the woods,fields,hedgerows and by river sides.In the pasture fields grow daisies,buttercups,clover,toadstools and meadow vetchling.In the woods you will find primroses,bluebells and woody nightshade.In the hedgerows you will find dog rose,red campion and cowparsley.By the river side grow marsh marigolds,bull rushes and water mint. In our survey we found 40 different types of wild flowers and plants,which shows that pollution and crop spraying have not seriously affected them.
